# Loop 
# The Player will decide where to run
# The player will gather finanical support from either grass roots, corporate, or state backing.
# The player will hire a team.
# The player will announce his campain, vision, and mission statement
# The player will travel and do speeches
# Speeches will be minigames of memeory, timeing, and unexpected circumstances
# Occassionally, random events will affect the campain.
# At the designated time, the votes will be tallied and the player wins or loses. 
